data.description: Looking for an adorable 4-side brick ranch in a quiet neighborhood? Looking to be close to all the happenings? This solid build brick home on a basement close to Smyrna Market Village, Truist Park, Silver comet trail, Chattahoochee River Parks, Midtown, and downtown Marietta, with an easy commute to airport. Is just what you are looking for.     Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, basement with fireplace, enclosed windowed sunporch, Downdraft cooktop and open concept living!
